## Key Features

### Blog System

- Markdown-based blog posts with RSS/Atom feeds
- Category filtering and trending posts
- SEO-optimized with proper metadata
- Interactive client-side components for enhanced UX

### Portfolio Showcase

- Interactive portfolio with detailed case studies
- Timeline and career journey visualization
- Skills and technologies toolbox
- Animated gallery with slideshow functionality
- Accomplishments and achievements display

### Contact Integration

- Contact form with email templates and validation
- Lead management system with structured data
- Social media integration
- Interactive user feedback

### External Apps Integration

- Agoras app with privacy and terms pages
- GymControl license validation and token management
- External app links and previews

### Technical Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 14 with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with Styled Components
- **Content Processing**: Custom HTML renderer with Markdown support
- **SEO**: Structured data, sitemaps, RSS feeds
- **Analytics**: AdSense integration
- **Deployment**: Docker + Custom release scripts
- **Package Management**: Yarn with lock file

## Getting Started

1. Run `yarn install` to install dependencies
2. Run `yarn dev` to start development server
3. Check [README.md](mdc:README.md) for detailed setup instructions
4. Follow [coding-conventions.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/coding-conventions.mdc) for development standards

## Common Tasks

- **Add new blog post**: Create markdown file and update API routes
- **Add case study**: Create new page in [app/case-studies/](mdc:app/case-studies) with proper layout
- **Update portfolio**: Modify components in [components/Portfolio/](mdc:components/Portfolio)
- **API changes**: Update routes in [app/api/](mdc:app/api) and utilities in [lib/](mdc:lib)
- **Add interactive features**: Create client components in [side-effects/](mdc:side-effects)
- **Add external app**: Create pages in [app/apps/](mdc:app/apps)

## Troubleshooting

- **"Super expression must either be null or a function"**: Add `"use client";` to components using client-only libraries
- **Server/Client component issues**: Check [nextjs-server-client-components.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/nextjs-server-client-components.mdc)
- **Common debugging patterns**: See [error-debugging-patterns.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/error-debugging-patterns.mdc)
- **AdSense integration issues**: Check [side-effects/AdSenseBanner.tsx](mdc:side-effects/AdSenseBanner.tsx)
- **HTML rendering issues**: Check [lib/htmlRenderer.tsx](mdc:lib/htmlRenderer.tsx)
